FT  08 APR 92 / Election 1992: Tory scientist - Ballot Box
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
A lone scientific voice has spoken up to defend the Conservatives against a
barrage of attacks from researchers who say British science has declined
since 1979. Terence Kealey, a clinical biochemist at Cambridge University,
