<TEXT>
Andy Fraser is gleeful about his new role as managing director of the
advertising agency Collett Dickenson Pearce. Having spent the last 11 years
with Saatchi and Saatchi, 41-year-old Fraser thought it was time for a
change. And nowhere better to head towards than CDP, where his Far East
