their youngest ever managers. He speaks the musical Thai language
'reasonably', some achievement in view of his admission that he is
'tone-deaf'.
Fraser is one of a handful of key Saatchi executives who have departed in
recent months, though he goes without acrimony - 'I'll never have a word
said against them'.
