<TEXT>
A. P. MOLLER, the shipping, shipbuilding and oil and gas group, increased
annual net profits by 65 per cent to DKr1.92bn (Dollars 305m) from DKr1.16bn
and profits before tax by 36 per cent to DKr2.78bn from DKr2.04bn.
The boost to profits arose primarily from shipping, which doubled net
