FT  08 APR 92 / People: Appointments
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Norman Becker is appointed divisional director of HITACHI's consumer
electronics division; he moves from domestic appliances.
*****
Robert DeBarr is appointed a director of LAND SECURITIES.
*****
Hamilton Anstead, currently finance director, is appointed deputy md of
TAKARE; Ron Reid has joined from Price Waterhouse as finance director
designate.
*****
